frames.caption: A fierce warrior stands poised on the deck of a ship, holding a futuristic bow. She is clad in intricate armor, with a quiver of arrows on her back, and the stormy sea rages around her.
frames.description: The scene is set on a ship amidst a stormy sea. A warrior, dressed in detailed armor and equipped with a high-tech bow, is ready for battle. The atmosphere is tense and dramatic, with dark clouds and turbulent waves adding to the intensity.

frames.caption: A fierce warrior stands on the deck of a ship, drawing a glowing blue arrow in her bow. She is clad in intricate armor, with a large hat and flowing hair, poised for battle against a backdrop of turbulent seas and another ship in the distance.
frames.description: The scene depicts a dramatic and intense moment at sea, featuring a warrior preparing to engage in combat. The setting is aboard a ship, with another vessel visible amidst stormy waters.
